text:
Comments 
Your browser does not support iframes. Slugging designated hitter Alex Rodriguez appears on this five-minute MLB.com highlight reel more than any other player, but there were plenty of exciting moments from the Yankees ' 2015 season in the Bronx and elsewhere. 
Brian McCann hit a walk-off homer. Right-handed pitcher Michael Pineda struck out 16 Baltimore Orioles . Rookie first baseman Greg Bird hit two homers in a game. And many more. 
Which was your favorite from this season?
